<p><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/q/4553129/4279">When to use os.name, sys.platform, or platform.system?</a> suggests that <code>os.name</code> might be <code>'nt'</code>. <a href="http://stackoverflow.com/q/1387222/4279">Reliably detect Windows in Python</a> suggests that <code>os.name</code> is <code>'posix'</code>.</p>  <p>Is it <code>'posix'</code> or <code>'nt'</code>?</p>